    dc:description "Fig. 4. Amynthas munglongoides sp. nov., holotype. A: Male pore region, ventral view (mp = male pore; gm = gential markings); B, G: Spermathecae and accessory gland (amp = ampulla; dv = diverticula; ag = accessory gland); C, E: Intestinal caeca; D; Prostatic gland; F; Male pore region, ventral view; H: Spermathecal region, ventral view (sp = spermathecal pore). Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10476485/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

